properties.Name: InsuranceEvent
properties.Description:
A specific insurance-related event that is tracked or identifies the current status of a Policy or Policyholder.

Ex:
- Application Completed / Signed
- Application Presented
- Application Returned Rejected
- Application Sent To Home Office
- Insurer Makes Counter-Offer
- Pending Statement Of Good Health
- Policy Issued
- Premium Deposit Received With Application
- Receipt Given To Applicant
- Underwriting Process Initiated

Columns.Name: InsuranceEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Event.

Columns.Name: InsuranceEventName
Columns.Description: The name of an Insurance Event.

Columns.Name: InsuranceEventDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an Insurance Event.
